title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show APR-03-2014 THURS
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show APR-03-2014 THURS...PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program 4/3/14Thursday, April 03, 2014 




Glenn covers the Fort Hood shooting that took place this week 
            and sheds light on the lack of respect President Obama 
                  and others in America have for soldiers. 

Jon Cardillo of PsyOps joins the program to discuss the changing American voter
                          and his predictions of libertarian political success for 2014.

 Also, Matt Kibbe of FreedomWorks talks with Glenn about 2014 politics,
       FreePac and his new book 

         "Don't Hurt People and Don't Take Their Stuff." 


               That and more on The Glenn Beck Program!
